data.description: This 4 bedroom 2 1/2 bath home sits on 6 lots wih circular driveway. Interior has a fresh coat of paint thru out. Electrical has been updated and a brand new garage door has been installed.This corner lot has plenty of room to park boats and RV. Just one mile from great fishing and some of the best restaurants. Home is located in the center of all the fun! Just 7 miles from Port A and a hop, skip and a jump from Rockport and Corpus Christi.
